title: FS: Lot of 75 raw T206 commons - SOLD
author: t206hound

posts.post_title: FS: Lot of 75 raw T206 commons - SOLD
posts.post_content:
The lot has been sold.  Thanks Steve.

I'm selling these as a single lot of 75.  First, the good news: there are only three Piedmonts in this lot.  The bad news is that the other 72 cards are Sweet Caporal :rolleyes:

At this point, just make your best offer.  I plan to list these on ebay on Sunday night if I can't make a deal here before then.  Cards will ship insured with signature confirmation.  Feel free to make paypal credit card payment if you wish.
